CIDADE MARAVILHOSA-RIO DE JANEIRO
Dong Kingman, the award winning Chinese-American artist, travels the world sketching and painting the
beautiful, the monumental and the picturesque. His watercolors grace more than forty permanent
collections in the USA and abroad
RIO DE JANEIRO is the jewel of South America. Nowhere in the world is a city blessed with so much natura
beauty. Corcovado Mountain, crowned by the imposing statue of Christ the Redeemer, and Sugar Loaf
renowned for its magnificent beaches. Gavea Beach, the site of the luxurious Inter-Continental
Rio, and Copacabana Beach, with its mosaic walks, are world famous. Pan Am serves Rio daily from
New York, Washington, Miami, San Francisco, Los Angeles, and Houston
